# For loops tutorial
# For loops iterate over a provided sequence (lists, tuples, dictionaries, sets, strings)

# Iterates through 0, 1, 2, 3, 4 (for a total of 5 times in this case)

# Built with 4 main components:
# FOR keyword; Variable that will hold the iterating value; IN keyword; your sequence

for i in range(1, 6):
    print(i)





















